				<h2>Change exchange Name to be more Descriptive</h2>
<p>The name "AskDifferent" is downright confusing and not useful.</p>

<p>Change it to something more useful like:</p>

<p>AskApple</p>

<p>AskOSX</p>

<p>AskiOS</p>

<p>AskMac</p>

<p>AppleExchange</p>

<p>MacExchange</p>

<p>etc.</p>

<p>If the site is to remain about anything-apple, then I like AppleExchange. However, I feel the different devices/os's are different enough to warrant their own exchanges. I would like to see them broke out into an iOS exchange, and a Mac/OSX exchange.</p>

