<p>Any choice of name would be down to personal opinion and preference, but I think it's far better than any of your suggestions which are all too narrow in there descriptive ability  other than AskApple, which has trademark and copyright issues. Using "exchange" brings to mind Microsoft, to me.  As you can see, logos and slogans etc have to be chosen very carefully.</p>

